{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847924689,"sessionID":"ses_2873ba3c4ffeb7MUp3Zh7kOMgM","part":{"id":"prt_d78c8d8ff001Y85PO6MF30rQtU","messageID":"msg_d78c8d0fc001VbxaVRihnYrPqP","sessionID":"ses_2873ba3c4ffeb7MUp3Zh7kOMgM","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_23b6609680394a5b9f162f59","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-008/README.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-008/README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/workloadmanager  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ## Summary\n8: \n9: Implement sandbox garbage collection mechanism for periodic cleanup of idle/orphaned sandboxes in the pkg/workloadmanager module.\n10: \n11: ## Status\n12: \n13: - [ ] Scaffold directory structure\n14: - [ ] Design GC strategy and policies\n15: - [ ] Implement GC core logic\n16: - [ ] Add cleanup scheduling\n17: - [ ] Add unit tests\n18: - [ ] Add integration tests\n19: \n20: ## Notes\n21: \n22: See `notes/` directory for implementation notes and decisions.\n23: \n24: ## Source Files\n25: \n26: See `src/` directory for source code changes.\n\n(End of file - total 26 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n\n**Module:** pkg/workloadmanager  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S\n\n## Summary\n\nImplement sandbox garbage collection mechanism for periodic cleanup of idle/orphaned sandboxes in the pkg/workloadmanager module.\n\n## Status\n\n- [ ] Scaffold directory structure\n- [ ] Design GC strategy and policies\n- [ ] Implement GC core logic\n- [ ] Add cleanup scheduling\n- [ ] Add unit tests\n- [ ] Add integration tests\n\n## Notes","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR